      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SMOOTH BEAUTY (2) jumped from this same draw and led throughout to score (22.51) at Ballarat over 390m in a T3 RSTW. Looks the one to beat again. JULY SHE LIED (4) is generally an honest type in the frame at 14 of 42 starts but missed the placings last time when sixth (19.56) over 350m at Healesville. Goes very well from this box. Has a good overall strike-rate and can find the frame here. TOO COLD (8) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only a nose (23.42) behind Aston Jalapeno at Warragul. The form from his last run stacks up well. Must be included in calculations. JUMBUK DAMIEN (1) is worth including.",
